 * values.value_2_title => 价值2标题:text:Mobile Clarity
 * values.value_2_desc => 价值2描述:textarea:Layouts, routes, and controls should remain readable during quick Gin Rummy browsing on smaller screens.
 * values.value_3_icon => 价值3图标:text:💬
